===soil management===
# The sum total of all [[tillage]] and planting operations, cropping practices, fertilizer, [[lime]], irrigation, herbicide and insecticide application, and other treatments conducted on or applied to a soil for the production of plants. 
# The sum total of all operations, practices and treatments used to protect soil and enhance its performance.
# The branch of [[soil science]] that deals with the items listed in (1)and (2).